			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Mage is an excellent class to learn the game with. Especially if you aren't getting twinked out by someone to start with.
<br />

<br />
LDoN - You can wait on this expansion, but you'll probably find it worth getting sometime after level 30. Take your time and learn the world and class a bit.
<br />

<br />
GoD - You can wait for a long time on most likely.
<br />

<br />
Most importantly...look around, adventure and enjoy the game. Don't let all the overly depressed Mages affect your decision. We do have some issues in the high end (60+) game, but we are still very effective.<br />_________________<br /><center><i><b>Samsara</b></i></center></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
