				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Yes, make a Mage. They are great fun. If you like being able to do damage, while at the same time being able to do a bunch of fun and useful things for your group of friends, then Mages are one of the better classes to do.
<br />

<br />
If you have friends already in the game, and you want to make a character that compliments their playstyle and group makeup, then let us know what classes they are, and maybe we can give you some ideas for a class that would compliment them well.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=375146" target="_blank" class="postlink">Gojirax</a> - 65 Arch Lich
